<!--
  Notification status-bar icon. MUST be a white silhouette on a transparent
  background: Android masks notification small-icons by alpha and tints them, so
  a full-colour @mipmap/ic_launcher would render as a flat white square. This is
  the Ironbit barbell mark (matches the boot emblem): two outer collars, two
  inner plates, and the connecting bar.
-->
